<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>مات مؤيّد <span class="c2">(٤)</span> الدولة <span class="c2">(بن بُوَيه)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> بجُرجان.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(ومات ابن طُرخان الملحّن)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span> <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
